channel.description: 2023-07-07 JER - MP-33: Modifications to the ORC transformer to pull in the ORC-14 Order Call Back Phone Number from ORC-23 Ordering Facility Phone Number 2023-06-13 JER - MP-33: Modified To Alabama Non-Covid destination connector transformer to handle evaluating and deleting OBR-13 object instances with toString() of 'Not Reported' 2023-05-09 JER - MP-38: Modify the [Mass] Destination Connector to associate an filter to reference patient_state of MA and not CA and cleared the source HL7 msg template 2023-04-18 JER - MP-32 Remove the need to insert the BioCode SARS-CoV-2 coded value on destination connector: To Tennessee OUT SFTP - TEST 2023-04-14 JER - MP-33 Modified to perform a static replacement of Copia Observation Code with LOINC code 2023-03-14 JER - MP-22: Modification TN ORM Conformance State Requirement For OBX-15.1 remove trailing A and if COVID -> segment['OBX.17']['OBX.17.1'] = 'BioCode SARS-CoV-2'; 2023-03-13 JER - MP-22: Modify to include To Tennessee SFTP OUT - Test destination connector and the channel incorporated functionality to remove non-Detected for the Vagnitis Pathogen testing. 2023-03-01 JER - MP-28: Modify the Alabama SFTP destination connector which was a clone of the prior Alabama non-COVID channel appears to have an HL7 template (removed) applied to the connector configuration. 2023-02-28 JER - MP-11, MP-16: Create a filter to only allow Non-COVID State Reportable Results - Test Channel (Alabama) - created a test Destination Connector to be sent testing for 'To Alabama OUT SFTP - TEST' to validate. 2023-02-28 JER - MP-22: Modification to the TN related changes - Modification TN ORM Conformance State Requirement 2023-02-15 JER - MP-24: Disabled the Alabama Non-COVID TEST, Texas Non-COVID TEST, and Tennessee-TEST destination connectors as they do not need to be enabled at this time. (Glenda)Â 2023-02-14 JER - Modified the Tennessee Test Destination Connector Transformer script - Modification TN ORM Conformance State Requirement MP-22 2023-02-08 JER - Applied the Preprocessor evaluation script to evaluate validity of the inbound msg meets HL7 conformance filtered at the source connector filter (preprocessor,filter) 2023-02-08 JER - Cloned the Alabama COVID SFTP Destination Connector for use with Non-COVID Testing (TEST) 2023-02-01 JER - Modify source connector transformer on filename as it was added outside of Jira case, Jira case MP-16 is to rollback this request. 2023-01-23 JER - Imported the Test Destination Connector - Washington - MFT for the new SFTP service. 2023-01-13 JER - Modified to include the patient and order metadata to the Custom Metadata mapped from the Source Transformer 2023-01-13 JER - Modification to TX-COVID & Texas Non COVID - TEST destination Connectors JS transformer translates the incoming Texas HL7v2 ORU message into a complaint HL7v2 ORU schema format
